### 1. Login first
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "kaveesha@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Create a trip — paste the token from step 1's response
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/trips
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJjNWU2YTBkZC04ZWE1LTQwMDktYTY0NC1lYTViMTM0YzI3MjYiLCJpc3MiOiJsYW5rYW1hdGUiLCJyb2xlIjoiVVNFUiIsImVtYWlsIjoia2F2ZWVzaGFAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQyNzE0MTEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDI3MjMxMX0.tqxYIg3FCbh3VgrEWPXXuMCoCp1b61Q3GIl-YT9AZEA2UsKedwS4ezIZd_uv8Vpa5tGSvSQmaG5ERMfEc2UV3w

{
  "title": "My Sri Lanka Adventure",
  "startDate": "2026-08-01",
  "endDate": "2026-08-07",
